snippet.title: Primal Carnage Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Kill your way to the top of the food chain in Primal Carnage, a team-based multiplayer shooter/biter hybrid. 

Make these creatures extinct again, or switch to the dinosaur team and have the humans for lunch!

Buy Primal Carnage for PC: 
http://store.steampowered.com/app/215470/

Visit the official website: 
http://www.primalcarnage.com

Like us on Facebook:
https://www.facebook.com/Primalcarnage
